ham-utils
=========

Author: Clayton Smith
Email: <argilo@gmail.com>

This project is a collection of utilities that may be useful to
amateur radio operators.

wsjt-mail.py
------------

This Python script sends an email to you whenever activity occurs in
WSJT-X.  It is useful to alert you of sporadic E openings on the 6
meter band.
